snippet.title: Atlus USA Trailer: Baroque
snippet.description:
In a land left devastated by an unexplained wave of destruction, a mysterious dark tower looms over a troubled populace. Ascend beyond the scorched earth on your quest for truth.

For more information, please visit:
http://www.atlus.com/baroque
